What is a Merge Document? © 2015 Jenzabar, Inc.     You can use three types of merge documents to initiate the flow of communication within EX:  How are Merge Documents Used in EX? © 2015 Jenzabar, Inc.     The text is sent as an email merge document type to the mobile device.     Each cell carrier has a domain to which you can send text messages as an email. For example, for Sprint, the domain is “@messaging.sprintpcs.com”.     To send an text message, you would concatenate the phone number with the domain. For example, to send a message to a Sprint customer, the “To:” in the email might read  9105555555@messaging.sprintpcs.com .
